<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="護法" xml:id="gsz0818a19shiXuanChang"><lb
ed="T" n="0818a19"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0818a19"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>京兆福壽寺<persName key="A009180">玄暢</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0818a20"/><persName key="A009180">釋玄暢</persName>，字<persName key="A009180">申之</persName>，俗姓陳氏，<placeName key="PL000000016956">宣城</placeName>人也。<persName key="A009180">暢</persName>爰<lb
ed="T" n="0818a21"/>在弱齡，便持異操，戲則聚沙為塔，摘葉為<lb
ed="T" n="0818a22"/>香。<date key="j20150812015445" from-iso="+0805-01-01" to-iso="+0805-12-31">年九歲</date>，於涇邑<placeName key="PL000000017025">水西寺</placeName>依<persName key="A011959">清逸</persName>上人，教<lb
ed="T" n="0818a23"/>授經法。<date key="j20187332019097" from-iso="+0815-01-01" to-iso="+0815-12-31">年十九</date>，削髮。<date key="j20190982019463" from-iso="+0816-01-01" to-iso="+0816-12-31">二十歲</date>，往<placeName key="PL000000017165">福州</placeName>兜率戒<lb
ed="T" n="0818a24"/>壇受具足戒，聽掇律科，深得宗旨。新繒細<lb
ed="T" n="0818a25"/>縷，一染色佳，而往<placeName key="PL000000013239">越中</placeName>求聞異說。仰京室<lb
ed="T" n="0818a26"/><placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName>有<persName key="A001519">宣律師</persName>舊院，多藏毘尼教迹，因<lb
ed="T" n="0818a27"/>栖<persName key="A011952">惠正律師</persName>法席。自入<placeName key="PL000000042189">京華</placeName>，漸萌頭角，受<lb
ed="T" n="0818a28"/><placeName key="PL000000042189">京城</placeName>三學大德，益廣見聞。方事講談，遽鐘<lb
ed="T" n="0818a29"/>堙厄，則<date from-iso="+0841-02-08" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="+0846-04-25"><name>會昌</name></date>廢教矣。時<placeName key="PL000000042189">京城</placeName>法侶頗甚徬徨，<pb ed="T" n="0818b" xml:id="T50.2061.0818b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0818b01"/>兩街僧錄<persName key="A011953">靈宴</persName>、<persName key="A011954">辯章</persName>，同推<persName key="A009180">暢</persName>為首，上表論諫。<lb
ed="T" n="0818b02"/>遂著《歷代帝王錄》，奏而弗聽。由是例從俗<lb
ed="T" n="0818b03"/>服，寧弛道情，龍蛇伏蟄而待時，玉石同焚<lb
ed="T" n="0818b04"/>而莫救。殆夫武皇厭代，<persName key="A003667">宣宗</persName>在天，坏戶重<lb
ed="T" n="0818b05"/>開，炎崗息熾。<persName key="A009180">暢</persName>於<date notBefore-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612035056" notAfter-iso="+0859-09-10"><name>大中</name>中</date>，凡遇誕辰，入內<lb
ed="T" n="0818b06"/>談論，即賜紫袈裟，充內外臨壇大德。<persName key="A006571">懿宗</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0818b07"/>欽其宿德，蕃錫屢臻。乃奏修《加懺悔一萬五<lb
ed="T" n="0818b08"/>千佛名經》，又奏請《本生心地觀經》一部八卷，<lb
ed="T" n="0818b09"/>皆入《藏》。<persName key="A009180">暢</persName>時充追福院<!--找不到此地-->首領，又充<placeName key="PL000000042422">總持寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0818b10"/>都維那，尋署上座。<persName key="A009180">暢</persName>講律六十座，度法者<lb
ed="T" n="0818b11"/>數千人，撰《顯正記》一十卷，科《六<anchor xml:id="beg0818sgsz5"/>帖<anchor xml:id="end0818sgsz5"/>名義圖》三<lb
ed="T" n="0818b12"/>卷、《三寶五運》三卷，雖祖述舊聞，標題新目，<lb
ed="T" n="0818b13"/>義出意表，文濟時須。<date notBefore-iso="+0874-12-21" key="j20406372042521" notAfter-iso="+0880-02-17"><name>乾符</name>中</date>，<persName key="A006571">懿宗</persName>簡自上<lb
ed="T" n="0818b14"/>心，特賜<persName key="A009180">師</persName>號曰<persName key="A009180">法寶</persName>。<date key="j20407712040771" when-iso="+0875-05-04">二年三月二十一日</date><lb
ed="T" n="0818b15"/>示滅，俗齡七十九，僧臘五十九。弟子賜紫<persName key="A011956">惠<lb
ed="T" n="0818b16"/>柔</persName>大德<persName key="A011957">師遂</persName>、<persName key="A011958">宗紹</persName>，以<date key="j20408042040804" when-iso="+0875-06-06">其年四月二十五日</date>窆<lb
ed="T" n="0818b17"/><anchor xml:id="beg0818sgsz7"/>于<anchor xml:id="end0818sgsz7"/>長安邑高陽鄉<placeName key="PL000000042095">小梁村</placeName>。<date from-iso="+0877-01-22" key="j20414002041783" to-iso="+0878-02-09">四年丁酉歲</date>，尚書<lb
ed="T" n="0818b18"/>禮部侍郎<persName key="A011955">崔沆</persName>與<persName key="A009180">暢</persName>交分殊深，著《碑》述遺<lb
ed="T" n="0818b19"/>跡焉。</p>
